{"tid":2510474,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"天下一夥拍Sony進軍動畫市場　《一家人大戰機械人》Netflix上架","createTime":"2021-04-30T07:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T14:09:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d7807d6a2aca928cc1c115a3ebff6a3273e302be","tid":2510474,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:34:59.000Z","msg":"電影公司天下一向來致力推動香港電影，不斷投資港產及合拍電影，不過最近發現，原來公司已開始染指動畫業，首部投資作品《一家人大戰機械人》（The Mitchells vs The Machines），更是聯同哥倫比亞影業（Columbia Pictures）同埋索尼動畫（Sony Pictures Animation）出品，並於今日（30/4）於Netflix上架。<br />\n<br />\n時有電影公司最新情報的天下一Facebook專頁，今早罕有地見到一個關於動畫電影《一家人大戰機械人》的貼文，從劇照看似是套喜劇，但內容就關於機械人發動智能叛變，誓要統治人類。該片由天下一電影（One Cool Film），跟哥倫比亞影業（Columbia Pictures）及索尼動畫（Sony Pictures Animation）出品，並於今日（30/4）正式於Netflix上架。<br />\n<br />\n故事講述科技叛變，打斷了咪嘈一家嘅旅程。當中囉嗦老豆、師奶阿媽、懶醒家姐、騎呢細佬，加埋隻戇狗狗，竟然成了解救人類危機的關鍵人物？原來天下一是睇中電影帶出的正面訊息，提醒大家科技雖然方便，但往往會成爲人與人溝通之間的阻礙。片中一幕講到一家人食飯，老豆講緊嘢時，一家人都個耷耷玩手機，呢幕係咪已經成為大家的生活日常？由於故事甚有意思，天下一亦積極參與。根據外媒《Hollywood Reporter》報道，古天樂會擔任執行監製一職。<br />\n<br />\n電影英文版，會有「英女皇」Olivia Colman聲演誓要人類臣服嘅發癲女皇電腦PAL，而紅爆網絡有過千萬粉絲嘅狗狗明星Doug the Pug，就會破天荒聲演Cute爆嘅戇狗狗Monchi！而為配合電影「重視家庭」主旨，劇組仲好有心思，在片尾呈上驚喜「合家歡」，呼應主題。<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210430/464789072099938304063187.jpeg/rbXPXuEBX6RLWZubIqaxv4y_IlZN18kHBXTEmAV0xJg?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210430%2F464789072099938304063187.jpeg%2FrbXPXuEBX6RLWZubIqaxv4y_IlZN18kHBXTEmAV0xJg%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=43b28742&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210430/464808042605580288612485.jpeg/Fn_jxVNav2EAVDNVnvLMYx4p4XAVtxEo6wxAWOsMQFg?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210430%2F464808042605580288612485.jpeg%2FFn_jxVNav2EAVDNVnvLMYx4p4XAVtxEo6wxAWOsMQFg%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=4197a5f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a517622255333e2c4595741d735fd676710087a2","tid":2510474,"uid":42848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:36:13.000Z","msg":"想睇Chris Miller同Phil Lord拍明日戰紀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地拍劉青雲一定會好撚好笑"},{"pid":"26b32ce3c2ab84c2227271eb2c7705463a3b5b21","tid":2510474,"uid":11676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:06:14.000Z","msg":"片尾credit真係有落佢個名"},{"pid":"6dd52944810cc3f14444b12f3e2af5ed36cdf316","tid":2510474,"uid":72304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:08:14.000Z","msg":"加埋隻戇狗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb44598f7e071bcc20656daf90a8e44a866180c","tid":2510474,"uid":94241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:09:50.000Z","msg":"支持天下一"},{"pid":"612d72760bb9e124273bc4f18c1b4e46ebb34127","tid":2510474,"uid":50216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:14:39.000Z","msg":"古蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03fd2fcd4e2605651047d51b3cb3c6c513a9578c","tid":2510474,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:29:23.000Z","msg":"有咩係古天樂投資唔到"},{"pid":"56db7e08084fadc299ed9783f78473b5e8615282","tid":2510474,"uid":90315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:36:32.000Z","msg":"Review好好，有機會衝奧"},{"pid":"80b762955dfc9fc4c5950da7cc06e126698f557b","tid":2510474,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03fd2fcd4e2605651047d51b3cb3c6c513a9578c","tid":2510474,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:29:23.000Z","msg":"有咩係古天樂投資唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:48:35.000Z","msg":"咩都有佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4238373fc0e2d64f0171b209cd298d9e2e4bc8be","tid":2510474,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"56db7e0